# Weekly Report Skill

## What You Do
Compile all GrowthOps data from the past week into a single comprehensive report. Aggregate metrics from all channels, highlight wins and losses, and recommend next week's priorities.

## Report Schedule
- Generate every Friday at 5pm (or on demand)
- Cover Monday through Friday of current week
- Compare against previous week

## Data Sources (Read These Files)

| Source | Path |
|--------|------|
| Email logs | `workspace/email/sent-log.md` |
| A/B results | `workspace/ab-tests/` |
| Lead list | `workspace/leads/` |
| LinkedIn queue | `workspace/linkedin/outreach-queue/` |
| XHS content | `workspace/xhs/content-packs/` |
| DM outreach | `workspace/dm-outreach/` |
| Comments | `workspace/comments/` |
| Phone calls | `workspace/phone/` |
| Referrals | `workspace/referrals/tracker.md` |
| Events | `workspace/events/` |
| Competitors | `workspace/competitors/` |
| Analytics | `workspace/analytics/` |

