## Report Delivery
- Save to workspace (always)
- If Slack webhook configured: post summary to #growthops channel
- If email configured: send to team distribution list

## Monthly Report
On the last Friday of each month, also generate a monthly roll-up:
- Save to `workspace/reports/monthly/YYYY-MM.md`
- Aggregate 4-5 weekly reports
- Add month-over-month trends
- Include cohort analysis from analytics skill
- Add 30-day forecast based on current trajectory
